I would treat this as if we're founding a company, not creating a GitHub repository.

Rule #1

We are NOT writing prompts.

We are defining an organizational architecture.

Everything must be reusable.

Everything must be extensible.

Everything must be versioned.

Everything must be documented.

Everything must have ownership.

