Create It

Open your terminal.

mkdir continuum
cd continuum
git init

Now

mkdir -p \
.github \
assets \
examples \
tooling \
docs/{philosophy,governance,architecture,standards,research,playbooks,glossary} \
continuum/{constitution,governance,councils,workflows,templates,schemas,protocols,standards} \
organizations/frontend-force/{v1,executive,departments,councils,agents,knowledge,workflows,standards,checklists,playbooks,templates,research}

